    "description": "鲍里斯-火箭是冷战时期的苏联火箭，你们要独自保卫你们广阔的家园。将不得不与寒冷和狗熊作斗争，茹毛饮血才能生存，快速适应才是王道。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/526625afb12cc947d41cb94926cba491.avif?t=1716452957\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/d3d41a55bd2b711dc42c21707098dfce.webp?t=1716452957\" width=350 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/284b41a774475fb9dc4ae5381e29dbbc.avif?t=1716452957\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br><br>沉浸于在冷战时期的戏剧性氛围中。这是一个对国家的责任大于自身意见的重要时刻，请将你的血肉之躯奉献给国家。<br>只有这样，你，才能真正成为祖国的英雄。千万别让你的祖国毁于一旦！<br>誓死保！<br>对于一个苏联人来说，死亡永远不是借口！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/d49ddffa59a973c90bd4f56c429955e7.webp?t=1716452957\" width=350 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/6677c5f9d6d67ef02e539a0d68a5cb10.avif?t=1716452957\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br><br>鲍里斯的身体有极大的可塑性，他会不断提高自己的能力。完美，没有极限！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/bc350a581ecb3beaa3e6e494a9311472.webp?t=1716452957\" width=350 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/4506f5925c559e53cd0d31b8fcd1f3f3.poster.avif?t=1716452957\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/4506f5925c559e53cd0d31b8fcd1f3f3.webm?t=1716452957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>敌人的导弹缤纷多样。停滞不前不可取，唯有前进才能塑造成功!敌人的创造力超乎想象。凛冬将至，高科技金属，才是致命的核炸药。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/119f28096dcc78faa42fc09850d2ff89.webp?t=1716452957\" width=350 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/745495eb5e70c81e29158ea91a8645ee.avif?t=1716452957\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br><br>保护自己不受熊的伤害，这不仅仅是制作一瓶饮品，更重要的是，伏特加能阻止熊的侵袭。做几瓶吧！一瓶为了自己，一瓶给你的新朋友！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/9cdae5a66e94a52dc47695c294c6aa7b.webp?t=1716452957\" width=350 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/61f4104e21a5c739305851fc9d168be2.poster.avif?t=1716452957\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/61f4104e21a5c739305851fc9d168be2.webm?t=1716452957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>对未来充满信心。这至少会让你的敌人尊重你，或者至多让他永远沉默。工程上的奇迹，地狱般的力量和辉煌的结合-“斯捷潘”洲际弹道导弹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/0a996e6a5747ac86a9ceb610e8cd2b29.webp?t=1716452957\" width=350 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329080/extras/b240a8c4d359c5599be62f29b176b4fa.avif?t=1716452957\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br><br>单一的音乐让你感到厌倦了吗？或者你还有更喜欢的？<br>我们特别为音乐爱好者，准备了游戏内的自带播放器。<br>小巧而好用！",
